{"tid":453581,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"支那寶鱔稿創作比賽 首回合（星期五截止）","createTime":"2017-10-31T10:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T16:24:16.000Z","uid":41245,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03a84d7aa3091e9722efd4007a50b314ed6ae1df","tid":453581,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:06:31.000Z","msg":"有鑒於各大傳媒都爭相出鱔稿推廣支那寶<br />\n連登當然唔可以執輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n規則：<br />\n每人可創作推廣支那寶文章，次數不限，以一個回覆為一篇<br />\n可以使用「支付寶」或「微訊WeChat」作創作藍本<br />\n可假設任何情況，創作空間不限<br />\n建議曲線以提升文章趣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n準則：<br />\n以正負評為首要指標，若負評達<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>即時取消資格<br />\n正評數最多之十個可以進入次回合<br />\n<br />\n示範：<br />\n是噉的，我今日上東莞叫雞見到條大陸妹嘅相好大波，好似好好啪，1q500，我就膽粗粗上咗佢到，咦條女有啲貨不對版，對奶又細啲不過都係女，算啦，問佢點畀錢啦。佢話用WeChat，好彩我有準備，知道大陸啲錢仲污糟過條女個閪，文明大國用電子支付。<br />\n因為我未用過，當我仲係電話到整緊之際，佢畀咗條皮鞭我，我心諗，咦？免費加㗎？正喎<br />\n我用嚟fet咗佢一嘢，條女即刻黑晒面，用唔鹹唔淡嘅廣東話同我講「香港來㗎？用嚟綁住電hwa㗎」<br />\n之後佢搶咗我電話，綁咗係條鞭到。佢一除條褲，我就見到佢個閪到紋咗個qr code，原來個system係我一插落條女到就會扣一次錢。原來大陸嘅電子支付已經咁發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1bb6e4956490903d59c50fda28e073f0f82494","tid":453581,"uid":67237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37171ea397ff7f7bcc628361fe6977c317e4854a","tid":453581,"uid":140218,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"即刻駁咀"},{"pid":"1630daf1b670d2e8ab033e64de55d5085125d16b","tid":453581,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"推,等多啲人參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286ce32eb5f957b8ff839e9299f74f98312301e5","tid":453581,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f61a8d4015d00d787ac437cd1b05462632293978","tid":453581,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0854bd15d73614caacccf987a85ae14fc80a3365","tid":453581,"uid":33321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9ff7debb5e85697e55bef352117b56de2973ef","tid":453581,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"五毛高手如雲 點解冇人入嚟參賽<br />\n係咪嫌獎品唔夠豐富"}]}